35
00:08:59,458 --> 00:09:00,458
Come.

36
00:09:28,333 --> 00:09:30,013
Putting you through now.

37
00:09:31,583 --> 00:09:33,263
-Hello.
-SP Patiala, Sir.

38
00:09:33,583 --> 00:09:36,160
We found an application of a new passport,

39
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,285
