41
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,250
Sher Singh.

42
00:09:41,625 --> 00:09:45,202
But the passport is issued
in the name of Ude Singh, Sir.

43
00:09:45,292 --> 00:09:46,285
Name again?

44
