be prepared for a long conflict

153
00:25:47,792 --> 00:25:49,472
"of 3 years or more."

154
00:26:01,583 --> 00:26:02,952
Ladies and gentlemen,

155
00:26:03,042 --> 00:26:07,285
it is a great privilege for me to
be here to talk to you on behalf

156
00:26:07,375 --> 00:26:11,917
of the East India Association and
the Royal Central Asian Society.

157
00:26:13,792 --> 00:26:16,875
In the war that is at our door step,

158
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:20,417
