276
00:33:23,958 --> 00:33:26,292
Punjab '39...

277
00:33:26,708 --> 00:33:29,333
Punjab '33 here we go, this is the one.

278
00:33:38,167 --> 00:33:41,202
Well if he is our man and
he came in six years ago

279
00:33:41,292 --> 00:33:44,159
what the hell has he
been doing since then?

280
00:33:51,833 --> 00:33:53,250
Bring him down.

281
00:33:54,708 --> 00:33:56,388
You are coming with us.

282
00:33:57,125 --> 00:33:58,618
Sit down and shut up!

283
00:33:58,708 --> 00:34:01,508
-Who all have come from India?
-Sir, I did.

284
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:04,077
-When did you enter England?
-In January.

285
00:34:04,167 --> 00:34:06,083
Show me your passport!

286
00:34:09,042 --> 00:34:11,642
What do you know about this Sher Singh?

287
00:34:21,917 --> 00:34:23,083
On your feet.

288
00:34:23,708 --> 00:34:25,250
Are you Surat Ali?

289
00:34:29,583 --> 00:34:33,750
-Mr. Koppikar do you know this man?
-Yes.

290
00:34:34,167 --> 00:34:37,160
