00:46:19,833 --> 00:46:21,417
just a friend or

483
00:46:22,417 --> 00:46:24,417
maybe a little more than that?

484
00:46:24,917 --> 00:46:25,917
Hmm?

485
00:46:27,625 --> 00:46:29,758
Don't you think that's personal?

