of Indian soldiers
fighting for us in this war.

850
01:10:49,250 --> 01:10:51,250
Are there not, Prime Minister?

851
01:10:51,542 --> 01:10:52,833
Yes there are.

852
01:10:54,125 --> 01:10:55,792
A meek surrender

853
01:10:56,208 --> 01:10:57,625
to this mad man

854
